Package: sjrdata
Type: Package
Title: SCImago Journal & Country Rank Data, Ready for R
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ilya", "Kashnitsky", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ilya.kashnitsky@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1835-8687")),
    person("Rob", "Hyndman", role = c("ctb"), email = "Rob.Hyndman@monash.edu", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2140-5352"))
    )
Maintainer: Ilya Kashnitsky <ilya.kashnitsky@gmail.com>
Description: SCImago Journal & Country Rank provides valuable estimates of 
    academic journals' prestige. The data is freely available at 
    <https://www.scimagojr.com> and is distributed for deeper analysis in forms of
    .csv and .xlsx files. This package pool them all together, ready to be used 
    in R.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    tidyverse
